1. *Odemo* u grad (We will go to the city).
2. Dogovorili smo se da *odem*o kući (We agreed to go home).
3. Ne mogu da *ode*m čak i da želim (I can't go even if I wanted to).
4. *Ode*li smo pre nekoliko sati (We left a few hours ago).
5. Njih dvoje su *odeli* u Srbiju (The two of them went to Serbia).